            "title": "Cryptocurrencies see fluctuations as Bitcoin's price drops to $111,246.07 and Ethereum slips to $4,321.10. Institutional interest wavers, with outflows seen in Bitcoin and Ethereum linked ETFs. Over $290 million liquidated, with $223 million lost by long-position traders. Bitcoin's open interest also dropped by 1.25% in the last 24 hours.",
